[38;5;234;3mQuickonf[0m[38;5;234m is a semi-automatic configuration tool for Linux desktop computers, allowing you to reinstall your Linux system and quickly get your favorite environment back.                                                                                                                                                               [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
